title: "MLSysim: A Composable Analytical Framework for Machine Learning Systems"
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: "Janapa Reddi"
    given-names: "Vijay"
    orcid: "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-5005-2564"
    affiliation: "Harvard University"
